title: thirdparty devices
extract: Example: "Several third party disk utilities are available for both Mac and Windows computers." Third party software refers to software programs developed by companies other than the operating system developer. ... Examples of third party components include hard drives, video cards, memory modules, and peripheral devices.Jun 27, 2009
